than one correct answer, enter a comma 
separated list of points.

`x-`intercept(s): [_______________]{"($b+$c/$a,0),($b-$c/$a,0)"} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("points") @]*  
`y-`intercept(s):  [_______________]{$yint} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("points") @]*

END_PGML


